data.description: so many upgrades making this home feel like new! The home welcomes you with high ceilings, fresh paint through out, new Lvp floors and lots of natural light. The kitchen faces the fully fenced backyard with privacy deck. upstairs you will find 3 bedrooms, with two full bathrooms. The second level can be used as an office, play area for the kids or anything you can imagine, it also has a half bathroom. The lower level can also be used for anything you can think off, currently being used as a gym and extra storage.Security system stays. Choice Home Warranty in place and is transferable. for more upgrades please refer to list. Welcome home!
